  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Game Play Streaming and Video Production Guide]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Modifying game code or manipulating game contents by <strong><u>reverse engineering, hacking</u></strong>, etc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Claiming that the content is <strong><u>officially approved and produced without prior consultation</u></strong> with the development team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you comply with the above, we allow disclosure and monetization through video production or streaming <strong>regardless of individuals or corporations.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please<strong> post a link to the store page in the outline column. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience the Joy of Puzzle Solving by Changing Pa!nt’s Colors!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/43a7fedded2114b356b485cf12674e47.avif?t=1755662850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras_big/43a7fedded2114b356b485cf12674e47.avif?t=1755662850 width=800 height=291 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey in <strong>\"Pa!nt\"</strong> begins in  the <i>Doodle world</i>. You will embark on a journey into the Doodle world alongside your small and adorable friend, <i>Moonie</i>, who was born from doodles in the notebook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve stages filled with puzzles made from doodles together with <i>Moonie</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each notebook is composed of stages built around Gimmicks that follow a specific theme. Challenge yourself with new Gimmicks and stages in every notebook!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet Our Friend, Moonie</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6dc3b7a32f86cf13323d6efd8cf1b653.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=560 height=315 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6dc3b7a32f86cf13323d6efd8cf1b653.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Moonie</i> is a small and adorable octopus doodle born in the Doodle world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moonie can pass through areas of the same color but not through different colors.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/488e500d1f36a4d2d1f76d283499daa5.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/488e500d1f36a4d2d1f76d283499daa5.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/488e500d1f36a4d2d1f76d283499daa5.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Change Moonie's color!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bda21f5b5752cf2ce1bff172fba10d6e.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bda21f5b5752cf2ce1bff172fba10d6e.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bda21f5b5752cf2ce1bff172fba10d6e.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry if <i>Moonie</i> can’t pass through a different color—just use a paint bucket to change Moonie's color!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Home Screen You Design Yourself</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/31e9bc322a0fa213ca24218e4174b803.avif?t=1755662850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras_big/31e9bc322a0fa213ca24218e4174b803.avif?t=1755662850 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Moonie’s Page</i> in <i>Pa!nt</i> is another world that you can create yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you clear more notebooks, the once plain notebook will become more vibrant and colorful!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four Special Gimmicks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/f3c2323e5376227d4d8f439da162fa9d.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/f3c2323e5376227d4d8f439da162fa9d.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/f3c2323e5376227d4d8f439da162fa9d.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The notebooks in <i>Pa!nt</i> each have their own special Gimmicks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the basic paint, you can discover a total of four new Gimmicks in <i>Pa!nt</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Gimmick can change <i>Moonie</i>’s color, move <i>Moonie</i> around, and add more fun to the puzzles. Experience the various Gimmicks and solve puzzles using them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, play through the notebooks to unlock the Gimmicks and customize your own notebook!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>60 Stages and Endless Content with the Map Editor</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=496 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Pa!nt</i>, you can currently explore a total of 60 stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the various Gimmicks you earn while playing through all the stages to create your own unique page!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just about playing alone—enjoy the experience together by creating and sharing stages, and immerse yourself in the charm of <i>Pa!nt</i>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Try out the new \"Black and White\" mode in <i>Pa!nt</i>.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy puzzles designed around colors, but experience them without the colors! Even though it’s monochrome, the unique fun of \"Black and White\" mode will surely keep you entertained!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>As you play through various stages, decorate Moonie!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/67a281e6686f481f0ed19349a201bb05.avif?t=1755662850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras_big/67a281e6686f481f0ed19349a201bb05.avif?t=1755662850 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While traveling through different stages in <i>Pa!nt</i>, you'll eventually earn a variety of outfits. Use the clothes you collect to customize <i>Moonie</i> and make it truly one of a kind!</p>",
