\" ><strong>60 Stages and Endless Content with the Map Editor</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=496 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/bcfbc0aa33f63989af5c6527ee9d9940.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Pa!nt</i>, you can currently explore a total of 60 stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the various Gimmicks you earn while playing through all the stages to create your own unique page!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just about playing alone—enjoy the experience together by creating and sharing stages, and immerse yourself in the charm of <i>Pa!nt</i>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Try out the new \"Black and White\" mode in <i>Pa!nt</i>.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.poster.avif?t=1755662850\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.webm?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/6456b7a04de3f4c7b972363c3ba55eb9.mp4?t=1755662850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy puzzles designed around colors, but experience them without the colors! Even though it’s monochrome, the unique fun of \"Black and White\" mode will surely keep you entertained!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>As you play through various stages, decorate Moonie!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras/67a281e6686f481f0ed19349a201bb05.avif?t=1755662850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516270/extras_big/67a281e6686f481f0ed19349a201bb05.avif?t=1755662850 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While traveling through different stages in <i>Pa!nt</i>, you'll eventually earn a variety of outfits. Use the clothes you collect to customize <i>Moonie</i> and make it truly one of a kind!</p>",
